                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable E</hi> 35.) The female prisoner took me to her house, No. 24, Frances-street, Tottenham-count-road—I there found various articles, which I produce—I did not take them at the time I took her, but afterwards, when I went to search her place—when I first went, it was with regard to another charge—she was not there when I took these things, and I never said anything to her about them.</p>
